==English==

===Adjective===
'''imponderable'''

# Not [[ponderable]]; without [[sensible]] or [[appreciable]] [[weight]]; incapable of being weighed.

===Noun===
'''imponderable'''

# {{physics}} An imponderable [[substance]] or [[body]]; specifically, in the plural, a name formely applied to [[heat]], [[light]], [[electricity]], and [[magnetism]].

